com.vmware.esx.settings.depots

Interface Umds

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Service, UmdsTypes
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    UmdsStub

    public interface Umds
extends Service, UmdsTypes
    The Umds interface provides methods to manage VMware vSphere Update Manager Download Service (UMDS) software depots used during ESX lifecycle management. This is the depot downloaded using UMDS.

    If a UMDS depot is specified then online depots are ignored and data is downloaded only from the UMDS depot.
